'''待用餐'''（{{lang-en|suspend meal}}）是指善心人士提前支付了一份餐點或飲品的價錢，以讓[[貧困|貧困]]或其他有需要者可以享用餐點的一种[[慈善|慈善]]行动和文化。待用餐文化起源於[[義大利|義大利]][[拿坡里|拿坡里]]的一間[[咖啡店|咖啡店]]，稱為'''待用咖啡'''（{{lang-it|caffè sospeso}}），<ref name="from it">{{cite web|url=http://udn.com/NEWS/NATIONAL/NATS4/7877639.shtml|title=歐洲待用咖啡 起源自義大利|author=蔡容喬|publisher=[[聯合報|聯合報]]|accessdate=2013-05-06|date=2013-05-06}}</ref>，也称“分享咖啡”<ref name="anntw">{{cite web|url=http://anntw.com/awakening/news_center/show.php?itemid=39996|title=保加利亞「分享咖啡」 免費提供溫情|publisher=[[台灣醒報|台灣醒報]]|accessdate=2013-05-08|date=2013-03-26}}{{dead link|date=2018年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>而這間咖啡店的消費者多為[[工人階級|工人階級]]。當某個人遇到好事後，他就会在咖啡店付兩杯咖啡的錢，但只拿走一杯咖啡，之後如果有人需要即可免費獲得一杯咖啡。<ref name="espresso">{{cite web|url=http://www.theage.com.au/news/entertainment/epicure/espresso/2009/04/20/1240079594155.html|title=Espresso: Coffee goodness|author=Larissa Dubecki|publisher=[[世紀報|世紀報]]|accessdate=2013-05-06|date=2009-04-20|language=en|archive-date=2018-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180120091853/http://www.theage.com.au/news/entertainment/epicure/espresso/2009/04/20/1240079594155.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="free">{{cite web|url=http://www.sofiaecho.com/2012/02/21/1770809_free-coffee-anyone|title=Free coffee, anyone?|author=Alyona Zhuk|publisher=The Sofia Echo|accessdate=2013-05-06|date=2012-02-21|language=en|archive-date=2016-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917002926/http://www.sofiaecho.com/2012/02/21/1770809_free-coffee-anyone|dead-url=no}}</ref>至今也已有許多國家的咖啡店举行和參與了这种活動。<ref name="from it" />，後續擴大到其他餐點或飲品。<ref>[http://www.ntdtv.com.tw/b5/20180328/video/218162.html?%E8%87%BA%E7%81%A3%E5%90%B9%E8%B5%B7%E5%BE%85%E7%94%A8%E9%A4%90%E9%A2%A8%E6%BD%AE%20%E6%82%A8%E9%9F%BF%E6%87%89%E9%81%8E%E5%97%8E%EF%BC%9F 臺灣吹起待用餐風潮 您響應過嗎？]</ref>

==歷史==
待用餐的起源是待用咖啡，一則2010年的報導指出這項傳統早在100年前就已經存在，但在意大利[[意大利經濟奇蹟|經濟奇蹟]]時期銳減，剩下上流社會人士在[[聖誕節|聖誕節]]期間會進行此項活動。<ref name="break">{{cite web|url=http://www.accessitaly.com/post/italian-coffee-break-part-1-e28094-paying-it-forward-in-naples.aspx|title=Italian Coffee Break part 1 — Paying it Forward in Naples|publisher=Access Italy|accessdate=2013-05-07|date=2010-04-07|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130331040125/http://www.accessitaly.com/post/italian-coffee-break-part-1-e28094-paying-it-forward-in-naples.aspx|archive-date=2013-03-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>另一則2008年的文章則認為此活動在當時已過時，作者訪問了三家咖啡店都已經至少15年沒有進行過這項活動。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://corrieredelmezzogiorno.corriere.it/campania/a_tavola/articoli/2008/10_Ottobre/06/caff%C3%A8_sospeso.shtml|title=Caffè sospeso, tradizione «sospesa» a un filo Rischia di scomparire la tazzulella benefica|publisher=[[晚郵報|晚郵報]]|accessdate=2013-05-07|language=it|archive-date=2013-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130516061425/http://corrieredelmezzogiorno.corriere.it/campania/a_tavola/articoli/2008/10_Ottobre/06/caff%C3%A8_sospeso.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

義大利文中「{{lang|it|sospeso}}」這個詞是由義大利作家{{link-en|路西安諾·狄克萊仙佐|Luciano De Crescenzo}}在一篇文章《{{lang|it|Il caffe sospeso: Saggezza quotidiana in piccoli sorsi}}》中所創造的，而這篇文章也推廣了這個消失已久的老文化。<ref name="free" /><ref>{{cite book|author=Luciano De Crescenzo|title=Il caffè sospeso|date=2010-10-07|publisher=Edizioni Mondadori|language=it|isbn=9788852014161}}</ref>2010年時的一份報導稱[[拿坡里足球俱樂部|拿坡里足球俱樂部]]的主席{{link-en|奧瑞里歐·狄羅倫提斯|Aurelio De Laurentiis}}還因球隊獲得勝利而捐出10杯待用咖啡。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.italymag.co.uk/italy/napoli/buon-compleanno-gambrinus|title=Buon Compleanno, Gambrinus|author=Pat Eggleton|publisher=Italy Magazine|accessdate=2013-05-07|date=2010-05-04|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130126194015/http://italymag.co.uk/italy/napoli/buon-compleanno-gambrinus|archive-date=2013-01-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>之後這個文化在[[保加利亞|保加利亞]]<ref name="anntw" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.news24.com/World/News/Bulgarian-cafes-get-an-Italian-twist-20130325|title=Bulgarian cafés get an Italian twist|publisher=[[法新社|法新社]]|accessdate=2013-05-07|date=2013-03-25|language=en|archive-date=2017-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170606233628/http://www.news24.com/World/News/Bulgarian-cafes-get-an-Italian-twist-20130325|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[基輔|基輔]]<ref name="free" />、[[墨爾本|墨爾本]]<ref name="espresso" />、[[魁北克|魁北克]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lapresse.ca/le-soleil/vivre-ici/societe/201304/11/01-4640087-un-premier-cafe-en-attente-a-quebec.php|title=Un premier «café en attente» à Québec|author=Claudette Samson|publisher=La Presse|accessdate=2013-05-07|date=2013-04-12|language=fr|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304081158/http://www.lapresse.ca/le-soleil/vivre-ici/societe/201304/11/01-4640087-un-premier-cafe-en-attente-a-quebec.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>、及[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.ruvr.ru/2012/01/07/63427265/|title=Coffee free of charge|author=Milena Faustova|publisher=[[俄羅斯之聲|俄羅斯之聲]]|accessdate=2013-05-07|date=2012-01-07|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523041404/http://english.ruvr.ru/2012/01/07/63427265/|archive-date=2013-05-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>等地被報導並傳開。2011年聖誕節時[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]還有捐贈咖啡享受折扣的風潮。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.at5.nl/artikelen/73480/caffe-sospeso-voor-inloophuizen|title=Caffè Sospeso voor inloophuizen|author=Dennis Hompes|publisher=AT5|accessdate=2013-05-07|date=2011-12-21|language=nl|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303225806/http://www.at5.nl/artikelen/73480/caffe-sospeso-voor-inloophuizen|dead-url=no}}</ref>英國的[[星巴克|星巴克]]在2013年4月主動推出待用咖啡的活動，不過星巴克會將咖啡換成等值的現金捐贈給英國慈善團體{{link-en|綠洲信賴|Oasis Trust}}。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.marketingmagazine.co.uk/article/1177756/Starbucks-joins-Suspended-Coffee-homeless-initiative|title=Starbucks joins Suspended Coffee homeless initiative|author=John Reynolds|publisher=Marketing Magazine|accessdate=2013-05-08|date=2013-04-10|language=en|archive-date=2016-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408080353/http://www.marketingmagazine.co.uk/article/1177756/starbucks-joins-suspended-coffee-homeless-initiative|dead-url=no}}</ref>英國的一些咖啡店也因舉辦待用咖啡的活動受到新聞媒體的報導。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/magazine-22267613|title=Would you buy a 'suspended coffee' for someone in need?|author=Suraj Patel|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|accessdate=2013-05-08|date=2013-04-23|language=en|archive-date=2016-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161209154707/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/magazine-22267613|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年1月，德國有心人士在[[Facebook|Facebook]]上創立「Suspended Coffees」（待用咖啡）粉絲專頁，吸引超過80,000人按「讚」。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/SuspendedCoffeess|title=Suspended Coffees|publisher=[[Facebook|Facebook]]|accessdate=2013-05-08|archive-date=2022-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220130164557/https://www.facebook.com/SuspendedCoffeess/|dead-url=no}}</ref>此專頁亦在各國善心人士支援下創立許多當地版本的專頁，吸引世界各地的人注意。

==象徵==
在[[2007年－2008年環球金融危機|環球金融危機]]與[[歐債危機|歐債危機]]期間，待用咖啡被視為是基層社會團結的象徵。<ref name="break" />2004年，一個慈善機構龍德慈善（{{lang|it|Ronde della carita}}）在[[復活節|復活節]]舉辦了{{lang|it|giornata nazionale del sospeso}}待用咖啡慈善活動。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nove.firenze.it/vediarticolo.asp?id=a4.04.12.08.29|title=Oggi giornata nazionale del caffé "sospeso"|publisher=Nove.Firenze.it|accessdate=2013-05-08|date=2004-04-12|language=it|archive-date=2014-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222150554/http://www.nove.firenze.it/vediarticolo.asp?id=a4.04.12.08.29|dead-url=no}}</ref>2010年，義大利幾個著重於人權的藝術節慶上都舉辦了{{lang|it|Rete del Caffè Sospeso}}慈善活動。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.retedelcaffesospeso.com/principi/|title=Principi|accessdate=2013-05-08|language=it|archive-date=2020-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200117191610/http://www.retedelcaffesospeso.com/principi/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2011年12月，{{lang|it|Giornata del Caffè Sospeso}}慈善活動在[[國際人權日|國際人權日]]上舉行。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cinemaitaliano.info/news/10505/la-voce-del-corpo-di-luca-vullo-in-tour.html|title="La Voce del Corpo" di Luca Vullo in tour|publisher=CinemaItaliano.info|accessdate=2013-05-08|date=2011-11-29|language=it|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304030346/http://www.cinemaitaliano.info/news/10505/la-voce-del-corpo-di-luca-vullo-in-tour.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>還有一個網站「1café.org」專門籌募待用咖啡。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.1caffe.org/|title=1Caffe|accessdate=2013-05-08|language=it|archive-date=2022-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220218144022/https://www.1caffe.org/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.greenews.info/rubriche/una-iena-piu-verde-che-nera-intervista-a-luca-argentero-20111223/|title=Una Iena più verde che nera. Intervista a Luca Argentero|author=Francesca Fradelloni|publisher=Greennews.info|accessdate=2013-05-08|date=2011-12-23|language=it|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322215737/http://www.greenews.info/rubriche/una-iena-piu-verde-che-nera-intervista-a-luca-argentero-20111223/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==待用餐慨念的擴張==
2013年4月，[[台灣|台灣]]及[[中國大陸|中國大陸]]部分地區亦將待用咖啡衍生成「待用餐點」，使窮苦人家可享用免費餐點，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nownews.com/2013/04/30/91-2931294.htm|title=你吃飯我付錢！　兩岸多家餐廳跟進「待用餐」善舉|publisher=[[今日新聞網|今日新聞網]]|accessdate=2013-05-08|date=2013-04-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://epaper.subaonet.com/sr/html/2013-04/22/content_311021.htm|title=Give if you wish, get if you want|publisher=蘇州日報|accessdate=2013-05-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303221301/http://epaper.subaonet.com/sr/html/2013-04/22/content_311021.htm|archivedate=2016-03-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20130416/34954632|title=陝西台商 推「待用餐」濟貧<small>河南重慶多家餐廳也跟進</small>|publisher=[[蘋果日報|蘋果日報]]|accessdate=2013-05-08|date=2013-04-16|archive-date=2016-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160312015451/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20130416/34954632/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 同時[[香港|香港]]更衍生出「待用券」，讓有需要的人憑券換領餐點。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130510/18255404|title=待用券興起　撐基層　幫小店|publisher=香港[[蘋果日報|蘋果日報]]|accessdate=2013-05-10|date=2013-05-10|archive-date=2015-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150915191331/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130510/18255404|dead-url=no}}</ref>

有動物保護團體推出「寵物待用餐」使流浪寵物維持生存的基本需求。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://udn.com/NEWS/LIFE/LIF8/7880027.shtml|title=寵物待用餐救急 不要棄養牠|publisher=[[聯合新聞網|聯合新聞網]]|accessdate=2013-05-08|date=2013-05-07}}</ref>[[台中市政府|台中市政府]]亦成立「待用食物平台」方便民眾捐贈待用餐，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ettoday.net/news/20130502/200957.htm|title=每個月5萬元買1000份待用餐　賴大東行善14年捐千萬|publisher=[[ETtoday|ETtoday]]|accessdate=2013-05-08|date=2013-05-02|archive-date=2013-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605022723/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20130502/200957.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://udn.com/NEWS/SOCIETY/SOC5/7857072.shtml|title=不讓待用餐閒置 中市開平台|publisher=[[聯合新聞網|聯合新聞網]]|accessdate=2013-05-08|date=2013-04-26|archive-date=2013-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130430070843/http://udn.com/NEWS/SOCIETY/SOC5/7857072.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>但各地多數餐廳還是呈現「捐多吃少」的情況。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.cts.com.tw/cts/general/201304/201304251232253.html|title=捐的多.吃的少! "待用餐"等嘸人|publisher=[[華視|華視]]|accessdate=2013-05-08|date=2013-04-25|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310103523/http://news.cts.com.tw/cts/general/201304/201304251232253.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://web.pts.org.tw/php/news/pts_news/detail.php?NEENO=238700|title=宣導.自尊心因素 "待用餐"難送出|publisher=[[公共電視台|公共電視]]|accessdate=2013-05-08|date=2013-04-24}}</ref>

